This PR adds git tag verification to the standard-versions autogen script to ensure the script is run from the correct commit when generating version metadata for the Superchain Registry.

To test: 

1. tag a commit: `git tag test-tag`
2. run the script: 

```
go run ./scripts/autogen/standard-versions --release mytest --opcm 0x6af7ece7d6506be573841b8cf29096638df5fc4f --rpc-url $SEP_RPC_URL

